When you “arrive”, it’s easy to fall off.. good things happen so, you become lazy, fulfilled and complacent. 

Same goes for when things go bad in life… you become depressed, angry and slothful. 

I’ve felt both the highs and lows. Truthfully, they both can equally consume you. If you aren’t prepared to adapt to what you’re going after, whether it’s good or bad, it will most likely change you and most often, not for the better.

As for me, I’m always “just getting started”. Focused on the preparation.. not the destinations ☠️⚔️. You’ll feel the same, no matter the environment or circumstance. 

📸: @mr_manugram
